                    <task workspace="8in">
                        <statement>
                            <p>
                           Define <m>f: \mathbb{R}\to \mathbb{R}</m> via
<md>
  f(x) = \begin{cases}1, &#x26; \text{if } x \in \mathbb{Q} \\ 0, &#x26; \text{if } x \in \mathbb{R} \setminus \mathbb{Q}.\end{cases}
</md>
Show that <m>\underline{\int_0^1 f}\lt \overline{\int_0^1 f}</m>.
